OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis staff to vote on
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffuture as anger grows      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of John Lewis will face a vote
OL,6, of confidence on Wednesday, amid       
OL,7, growing staff anger at her leadership. 
OL,9,FIt comes after Dame Sharon White was   
OL,10,Funderstood to be considering selling a 
OL,11,Fstake in the retailer, meaning it would
OL,12,Fno longer be fully owned by staff.     
OL,14,FJohn Lewis is seeking to revive growth 
OL,15,Fafter posting a huge loss last year and
OL,16,Fsuspending its staff bonus.            
OL,18,FBut as job cuts loom, employees may use
OL,19,Fthe biannual vote - which is           
OL,20,Fnon-binding - to push for change.      
